; BF++ TUI demo — ANSI escape sequences for terminal UI
; Prints a colored box using raw ANSI codes

; ESC = 27
; Print ESC[2J (clear screen)
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++. ; 27 = ESC... wait, need exact 27
[-]
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++  ; cell = 27
.                            ; print ESC
[-] ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ ; [ = 91
.
[-] ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ ; 2 = 50
.
[-] ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ ; J = 74
.

; Print "BF++ TUI Demo" with color
; ESC[32m (green text)
[-] ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++. ; ESC
[-] ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ . ; [
[-] ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++. ; 3
[-] ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++. ; 2
[-] +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++. ; m

; Print text
"BF++ TUI Demo\n\0"
<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<
[.>]
